channel.title: The Story Of Mopar By PriMaL
channel.description:
Please Actually Read it Toke Me Along Time To Write YoU Wont Fight This Any where Else Except My Website
A New God - PriMaL The Warrior ------------------------------------------------ A Small Adventurer Traveled The Land Of MoparScape Hoping To Start A New Life, He Trained And Fought. Ranged, Magic Or Strength, This Brave Adventurous, Defeated His Enemies Little Or Big He Still Courageously Toke Over The Land Of Edgevill, As The Day Dawned And The Feast Of His Victory Began The Darkness Arrived The Small Village Screamed In Fear As There End Was About To Come, Little Did These Villagers Know, One Day They Will Be Saved The Dark Evil Spirit Delreth Attacked The Village And Disturbed The Villagers, Slowly He Came To The Fort Of Edgevil There Lied Asleep The Small Child, His Name PriMaL. The Villagers Ran In Fear, Only One Remained The Brave Adventurous Gonthorian Fought Hard, He Used All His Strength To Fight Off The Evil Spirit Delreth But No Luck Was Found. At The Last Moment Gonthorian Remember His Masters Spell Vengeance Bravely He Sacrificed His Life In Order To Save The Life Of Another, This Man Is Named PriMaL. 34 Years Later.... ---------------------------------- The Young Man Primal Seated On The Throne Of Edgevill, Suddenly Receives A Message From The King Of Falador Saying "We Are In Danger The Land Of Falador Has Been Over Come By Deletes Minions! SAVE OUR SOULS!!" At Once Primal Arose From His Seat, Knowing His Destiny He Awakened The Grand Master And Begged For Wisdom, The Grand Master Iroh Casted A Spell To Spy On Delreth And His Minions, He Arose In Fear. PriMaL Had 4 Weeks To Ready Him Self For Delreth. The First Week..... --------------------------------- PriMaL Trained On Smaller Creatures He Mastered The Art Of Magic Casting High Spells Which Destroyed Villages And Even Cities, The Spells Were Called Waves All Formed From 4 Basic Elements, Air, Water, Earth And Fire. The Second Week --------------------------------- PriMaL Ran Across Edgevill Mastering The Art Of Archery, Aiming High And Succeeding In His Goals, Defeating Enemies From All Over The World Creating A Rapid Attack Sequence Which Fires 2 Arrows At Once. He Called His Bow, The Magic Short Bow. The Third Week -------------------------------- PriMaL Knew This Was His Last Week To Train Through Many Troubles And Tolls He Mastered The Art Of Battle, Melleing All His Enemies And Protecting His Land He Then Created A Sword Which Trembled The Lands And Seas And Used The Power Of The Sun To Burn The Bones Of His Enemies, He Called This Weapon, The PriMaL Long Sword! The land Of Edgevill Prepared For The Battle Of Their Lives, Small Or Big They Knew What Evil Lied Down The Streets Of Edgevill. The Battle ------------------------------- The Warriors Gathered For Battle The Strongest And Finest In The Front And The Weaker In The Back, The Dark Evil Spirit Entered The Village Of Edgevill And Spoke "Foolish Creatures Fear Me For I Have The Power To End You And Your Filthy Village" All The Warriors Stood Their Ground As An Act Of Appreciation To Their Leader. The Warriors Fought The Minions Of Delreth And Cruelty Defeated Them With No Trouble, Delreth Realised This Foolish Mistake And Casted A Spell Doubling The Population Of His Minions, At Once The Warriors Were Frightened By The Population Of These Evil Spirits And Backed Down Slowly The Numbers Of These Warriors Decreased From 10s Of Thousands To 5s And From 5s To Hundreds, Slowly The Weakest Of Them All Remained As For The Rest Of The Warriors, There Souls Had Been Vanished, PriMaL Bravely Fought Off The Minions, And The Only Two Things On The Battle Field Were The Brave Warrior PriMaL And His Nemesis Delreth The Evil Spirit. He Laughed And Spoke Vulgarly About The Father Of PriMaL. PriMaLs Anger Increased And The Fight Began. Primal Casted His Spells And Shot His Arrows Yet The Evil Demon Delreth Remained Un Scratched Finally Delreth Decided To Attack Wiping Out Half The Village And Half The Life Of PriMal. PriMaL Prayed To His Father Gonthorian Asking For Assistance, Yet Delreth Continued To Destroy The Village, Attacking PriMaL With No Hesitation. Suddenly A Yellow Light Appeared In The Sky, It Appeared To Be The Great Gonthorian The Father Of PriMaL. He Offered His Assistance And Spoke "My Son, Who I Am Dearly Proud Of Wield Thy Sword And Slay This Evil Spirit. PriMaL Wielded The Long sword And A Massive Glow Appeared, PriMaL Knew It Was The Time To Strike, He Bravely Stroked The Spirit Delreth And Slayed His Evil Soul, Saving The Land OF Edgevill. The Feast ---------------------------- The Land Of MoparScape Rejoiced In Their Great Victory And Prepared A Great Feast The Feast Which Filled There Souls With Happiness, The Castle Of Varrock Was Empty And Their Lied The Young Man PriMaL, Or Should I Say The Young God PriMaL - PriMaL The God Of Vengeance
